gov.usgs.anss.edgethread

Interface ManagerInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CWBCorrelationPicker, CWBFilterPicker6, CWBPicker, CWBSubspaceDetector, DatasockClient, FK, ISILink, LISSClient, NetservClient, ReftekClient, RingFile, RingServerSeedLink, RRPRingFile, SeedLinkClient

    public interface ManagerInterface
    This is the interface implemented by threads that are to be controlled by a manager process. Such processes need to be able to set a check flag in a process to track whether it has disappeared, a way to terminate the threads if they have disappeared, and to gather status from its children.
